#EXTM3U
# nothing-htpc curated cable lineup.
# Format: tvg-chno = the channel number on your "cable box".
# Numbers are stable — add channels at any free number, gaps are fine.
# 991-993 are reserved for teletext (defined in cabletv.lua).
#
# Sources: iptv-org (github.com/iptv-org/iptv), publicly available streams.
# [Geo] = geo-blocked to MK — works from home, not from elsewhere.
# Paste me more m3u playlists in chat and I'll extract + merge channels here.

